			News file for CCMemory
			======================

Revision 0.2.1-devel.4
----------------------

* Package infrastructure development.


Revision 0.2.1-devel.3
----------------------

* Fixed documentation of some functions using the standard allocator.

* Package infrastructure development.


Revision 0.2.1-devel.2
----------------------

* Development of build infrastructure.


Revision 0.2.1-devel.1
----------------------

* Development of ASCII and ASCIIZ string representations.

* BACKWARDS INCOMPATIBILITY Total review of memory blocks module.


Revision 0.2.1-devel.0
----------------------

* Added exception handlers and guarded memory allocators.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.1
----------------------

* Updated to CCExceptions v0.8.0-devel.4.

* Added missing C headers includes.


Revision 0.2.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Changed  API:  the  allocator's  free function  no  longer  raises  an
  exception.


Revision 0.1.0-devel.3
----------------------

* Added  missing URLs  for  dependencies to  the  documentation and  the
  README files.

* Updated to CCExceptions v0.8.0-devel.2 and CCTests v0.3.0-devel.0.


Revision 0.1.0-devel.2
----------------------

* Better check for CCTests in "configure.ac".


Revision 0.1.0-devel.1
----------------------

* Fixed data script for "pkg-config".


Revision 0.1.0-devel.0
----------------------

* Initial development release.


